{
 "name": "RPlog_Korolov_s_Senate_Bombing",
 "title": "Korolov's Senate Bombing",
 "summary": "As the New Republic Senate debates a controversial military bill, with Chief of State Leia presiding and General Enb'Zik Ikihsa speaking, watchers and Marines including Rook, Vengan, and Snarl keep an uneasy eye on the chamber while a Force-vision sends Luke Skywalker racing to the building. The moment the vote concludes, a chain of bombs tears through the Senate Chambers, immolating delegations and pods as Senator Viktor Faust is revealed to be the Sith Lord Korolov in crimson armor, his disguised stormtrooper Guards turning their weapons inward. Amid the collapsing dome, Luke duels Korolov while Rook commandeers a repulsor pod and the surviving soldiers -- Vengan, Kesander, Aramis, Rasi, and the wounded Snarl -- fight a desperate retreat. As Korolov initiates Plan Retribution, the battered pod barely escapes through a crumbling wall, leaving the ruined chamber behind.",
